OL,3,CWorld Rowing criticised for failing to
OL,4,Cremove topless women video from website
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Sports Producer Joe
OL,7,FWardropper, Sports Editor Steve Scott
OL,8,Fand Producer Esme Jones
OL,10,FWorld Rowing has been criticised for
OL,11,Ffailing to remove a video from its
OL,12,Fwebsite in which women were filmed
OL,13,Fsunbathing topless by a river during a
OL,14,FWorld Cup women's race, ITV News can
OL,15,Freveal.
OL,17,FThe footage, which was still available
OL,18,Fon the governing body's official
OL,19,Fwebsite on Wednesday afternoon, was
OL,20,Ffilmed during a race in Munich in the
OL,21,F1990s.
