OL,3,CWorld Rowing criticised for failing to
OL,4,Cremove topless women video from website
OL,6,FThe coverage twice cuts away from the
OL,7,Frace action to focus in on topless
OL,8,Fwomen, who are seemingly unaware they
OL,9,Fwere being filmed.
OL,11,FWorld Rowing was alerted to the
OL,12,Fexistence of the video almost a week
OL,13,Fago by Alan Sinclair, a former Team GB
OL,14,FOlympic rower, and European Champion,
OL,15,Fwho was reviewing old race footage as
OL,16,Fpart of his job as a coach.
OL,18,FSinclair told ITV News he was
OL,19,F''horrified'' by what he saw.
