OL,3,CWorld Rowing criticised for failing to
OL,4,Cremove topless women video from website
OL,6,FWhen first reporting the video to
OL,7,FWorld Rowing, Sinclair cited ITV News'
OL,8,Finvestigation into serious allegations
OL,9,Fat the world's oldest club, urging the
OL,10,Fgoverning body to act quickly.
OL,12,F''With the rowing world being in the
OL,13,Fnews in the UK... it is vital that
OL,14,FWorld Rowing sets an example by
OL,15,Frecognising - promptly - this issue,''
OL,16,Fhe wrote.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/7
OL,2,W,.!/  +.!/*%*%R,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
