OL,3,CWorld Rowing criticised for failing to
OL,4,Cremove topless women video from website
OL,6,F''I would have thought that World
OL,7,FRowing, as the international governing
OL,8,Fbody, would want to be setting a
OL,9,Fprecedent in making the rowing world a
OL,10,Fsafe, respectful and inclusive place
OL,11,Ffor all, especially with something
OL,12,Fthat should have been so easily and
OL,13,Fswiftly corrected. We can do so much
OL,14,Fbetter."
OL,16,FSinclair told ITV News he first
OL,17,Fcontacted World Rowing about the video
OL,18,Fon June 5 and received a reply on the
OL,19,Fsame day from its European President,
OL,20,FAnnamarie Phelps, who acknowledged the
OL,21,Fvideo was ''shocking''.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/7
