OL,3,CWorld Rowing criticised for failing to
OL,4,Cremove topless women video from website
OL,6,FShe then alerted a safeguarding
OL,7,Fofficer at World Rowing, who promised
OL,8,Fto ''coordinate with the
OL,9,Fcommunications team to determine the
OL,10,Fappropriate course of action.''
OL,12,FSinclair sent multiple follow-up
OL,13,Femails, with Phelps replying on
OL,14,FSaturday to say she had requested it
OL,15,Fbe removed ''immediately'', before
OL,16,Fadding: ''I suspect nothing will
OL,17,Fhappen until Monday.''
OL,19,FBut the video has remained live on the
OL,20,Fwebsite since.
