OL,11,FIn his email to World Rowing, Sinclair
OL,12,Fsaid their failure to act made him
OL,13,F''question how seriously you (World
OL,14,FRowing) are taking this situation.''
OL,16,F''The women being filmed deserve at
OL,17,Fthe very least the respect of the
OL,18,Fvideos being removed and that should
OL,19,Fhave happened yesterday'', he wrote, a
OL,20,Fday after contacting the organisation.
